He always tied in modern media and current events into his slides to make students relate to them. He was genuinely one of the best professors I've ever had. 10000% would take this class again.
Sweetest Prof ever. His class is really easy, but it's not less because of that. The content is informative and presented in an interactive, fun way.
THis time I only one thing to say. He is the best teacher I ever had. absolutely loved the AMAZING and MIND BLOWING interactive course notes!
I enjoyed the content. I thought the theories and lessons were very interesting and I was excited to learn more
Prof. Gauthier is very enthusiastic about the course content and is very clear on what the content would be each week. I am glad he put out weekly reminders to keep us on track.

One of the best professors I've ever had! The humour, enthusiasm, and level of knowledge Dr Gauthier has is incomparable to any other prof I've had before. There need to be more profs like Dr Gauthier. The lectures were my favourite part of the course and it definitely showed how much Dr Gauthier cares about his students.

LITERALLY A GEM!!!! If you read this comment, TAKE THIS PROF NO MATTER WHAT. HE IS AMAZING, HE IS HILARIOUS AND HE'S SOOOOO PASSIONATE ABOUT HIS WORK AND STUDENTS. I've never loved a prof more, his teaching methods are great and he answers emails so quickly. He encourages students and is so caring. I am so glad I took him twice before I graduate!!!

I enjoyed that this class was all online and no meetings were scheduled. Also the assignments were fair and doable!I have greatly enjoyed the prof enthusiasm and I hope to be his student in another class in the future.

Thank you Professor Gauthier for an engaging course! Your caring and consideration for your students is noticed! I wish all my professors developed their courses with as much care and passion as you did. In this difficult time you formatted your course in a unique way that took into account the diverse needs of your many students.
Loved the course! The materials were prepared in a very accessible and entertaining way. Enjoyed the several animations and visual component of the course.

I know how much effort and time it takes to make these interactive course notes because I tried making them for a project and man was it work!! I really appreciate the amount of work this professor put in to make content like this for us, the content was very accessible. Well done Professor I hope I can learn from you again one day!
This was an amazing course and I always felt interested. I really enjoyed the assignments and quizzes and felt that they accurately represented the course! Thank you for a great semester.

I normally don't learn well through completely online courses, however, his interactive course notes were very informative and interesting. Every time I sat down to start the course notes I would always finish since they were so entertaining. I really enjoyed how the course had structure in indicating where we should be in our work.

I really enjoyed this course. The assignments were fun and a good level of difficulty. It was great to have the pdf format of lectures and the video clips from movies on Brightspace. It was nice to have the textbook online. The movies we had to watch for class were really cool. Overall, this class was really cool and fun.

I really enjoyed taking this course with this prof! I like how, although it was an asynchronous course, it still felt very interactive. I really liked the creative aspect of the interactive course notes! It made it even more fun to learn about pop culture because you continuously had visual examples to accompany the content. Definitely recommend!

LOVE this Professor!! I took this course because he had such good ratings on rate my prof and I'm really glad I took this course as my elective! The format of the course was super cool, I've never had interactive notes like this and the format made the lecture plan and content super clear and organized!!
I loved the teaching style! Lectures were very clear and easy to follow while also being engaging. the perfect format for distance learning.

I loved this course. The teacher managed to make the course engaging and interactive while learning an interesting topic. I loved how easy this course was and how the prof always wrote emails with memes or gifs in them.

I really like the way prof Gauthier organized the notes. Rarely do professors even acknowledge the online resources as a viable option to teach, but Gauthier actually designed his notes to be both interactable and easy to read, which actually enhanced my learning and attentiveness by a lot. Gauthier uses the online space to its fullest capabilities

What I liked about the course was the organization and the effort put in by Professor Gauthier in letting students improve. There are numerous chances given for the weekly quizzes and for each assignment, there is a preliminary step which students use to get feedback from others and to give feedback. The prof and TAs gave good feedback.
I really liked the prof and the course. I loved the way the interactive notes were made, I loved going to his class. The class was so much fun and I wish I got 2 meet him one day in person!

His teaching style is always engaging. I am never bored during his lectures, not only because of the class's content but because of how he teaches it. I liked how he always made sure to reach out every week, even though the classes were all asynchronous. Overall, fantastic class and a fantastic teacher!

Prof. Gauthier is an incredibly engaging prof who is clearly very passionate about all things related to cinema. He made the class extremely fun and enjoyable. Most of all I appreciated the amount of effort he put in to making sure this course remained engaging during the pandemic. He was always very kind and understanding of his students.
I really liked the course. Professor was really enthusiastic. As a foreign student, it was really great that professor give students various format of teaching material.

It is clear that Professor Gauthier cares about his students. He is always excited to deliver course content and tries his absolute best to make it entertaining. The lesson modules are super fun and interactive.

I really enjoyed this course, as I didn't know what to expect from a course from a different faculty than my own (Science). The online modules were EXTREMELY well organized and fun to follow. The quizzes were nice as they gave us opportunities to test our knowledge without high stakes. Overall 10/10 for the course and the prof!

Best professor Ive ever had! Professor Gauthier used interactive course notes to make learning the materials fun. The assignments relayed very closely to the material presented in lectures and the TAs gave excellent and constructive feedback. 5 stars would definitely recommend taking any course with this prof.

I took this class as an elective and was not disappointed. Prof. Gauthier's class was super interesting and he was hilarious. The assignments were all very interesting, often allowing students to choose the direction they wanted to go or topics they were interested in. TA's feedback was also super helpful. Would definitely recommend this course.
Hes annoying and sort of rude
hes truly awesome and very positive. his charm makes the class really fun and makes u wanna go and learn

although the class was taught online the professors charm an humour was present. You dod have to teach yourself most of the content but through the creative interactive notes it was not hard. I would recommend this class for sure (uOttawa). I hope to see more from this prof in the future!

What are you waiting for?! Take his class (doesn't matter which one). Il est un prof dynamique et sincère avec ses étudiants. If you take the time to read your notes (only need the powerpoint), you don't have to worry, it's straightforward questions. I'm so happy to have taken his class before I left uOttawa - he made up for the awful profs I had.

If you want to laugh and have fun while you're learning, this is the prof for you. I was super excited that I got to be in one of his lectures again and I wasn't let down. He's also really easy going and understanding of other things that are going on in students' lives.
I would pay higher tuition just to have him teach all my classes

Great professor! I loved the lecture and how everything was made in the funniest way possible with a lot of cool features and resources. I would just suggest to the professor to read less the slides and maybe just talk more and promote debates. Overall he's super open and great, it's a fun class if you're interested in cinema/Sci-fi

Awesome professor! The course notes and updates are clear and very straight forward. He includes funny pictures and gifs making reading less boring. For an online class he made it exciting and entertaining!

Philippe is passionate about film and does a good job a relaying the content in an entertaining manner. He cares about the class and treats you like a person. If he is teaching a course and you can take it, go for it!
Coolest prof Ive ever had in my undergrad! His material is interesting and makes the lectures fun and hilarious ! Strongly suggest you take his classes
Professor Gauthier is great! He is just really great! Awesome professor and I really wish all my professors are like him...

Hands down the greatest professor to ever do it. He LOVES what he does and it shows in everything from the lectures which are an absolute blast to the exams which are straightforward and clear. He cares about his students and will help you gladly if you need it. Definitely going to take another class with Prof. Gauthier again. HE ROCKS!!!

Really enjoyed my lectures with Professor Gauthier. His excitement and interest in what he's talking about makes the content easy to follow and his humorous approach to lectures made me attend every week!

Great guy, absolutely hilarious. I was in one of his film classes that he taught in English and he doubted himself sometimes but honestly his english was 100% understandable and his lectures made complete sense- take home exams were from the lecture slides but he can throw in some tricky questions so read carefully. Great class and guy overall
It's rare to come across a professor who is as engaging and committed as he is. It is clear that he is passionate and interested in the material that he is teaching and he makes it very fun to learn!

Prof. Gauthier is a one of a kind prof. He is very fun and keeps things light-hearted in a film history course at 7pm at night. High energy and always means well. Always available through email and is very personable. He is a prof you should definitely try if given the opportunity. I know I well seek out his classes in the future.
Wonderful prof, very understanding of the stresses of being a student. Such a joker!

He is such a kind fellow. He has a very excitable personality so if you are not interested in having some fun in your cinema class than maybe find a more serious prof. Professor Gauthier is both very approachable and truly caring. I would take another cinema class simply to see him again. One whole-hearted recommendation!!!!!

The most hilarious and most kind professor I've had at Queen's so far. Course was very interesting due to his engaging teaching methods, and his caring personality made every student respect him. Amazing prof luv u

Best prof I've had at Queen's yet. He made the evening 3-hour lectures worth attending with his hilarious and energetic approach to the material. He genuinely cared for the success of all students, and was easily accessible at any time for questions.
He is the best ! Love his class.

I took this class as an elective and absolutely loved it! He made coming to class fun and enjoyable, and really wanted all his students to succeed. I would definitely recommend this class to anyone looking to learn more about Media and Popular Culture!
Passionate professor
Dr. Gauthier is one of the most hilarious, caring and genuine professors I've had at Queen's. He makes 3 hour lectures enjoyable and is super helpful and accommodating.

Professor Philippe Gauthier is one of the best professors Ive had at Queens University so far! Hes hilarious and jokes around while at the same time showing compassion for his students and wanting the best for them. 10/10 would recommend!
Excellent professor who puts in effort to make his lectures engaging for students.
Great class. Great prof.

Amazing guy

All professors should be as easy going, caring, and funny as this guy. He pretty much wants two things, for you to get an A and for you to have fun/laugh in his class. Can't wait to take another class with him.
AMAZING! Would for sure recommended this course, very fun and easy to do well!
The best prof i have ever had! He is so nice and helpful and HILARIOUS! I would recommend everyone take his class!!
10% extra to final grade for writing the USAT, describes his care for students perfectly

The class was made interesting by his unique lecturing approach! He managed to find a way to make 3 hour lectures go by slightly faster while making you remember the content you learned. He teaches a pretty fun subject but he makes it even more interesting! He's super funny and he's always willing to help! The class is pretty easy with 3 tests and a final essay. He's a fun guy and was always encouraging us in his emails to us about tests! Just take a class with him dammit!

Super awesome lectures that are fun and interesting. Be prepared to laugh. There are 3 exams throughout the semester and one final paper. It is all pretty easy as long as you know the material. The Prof is also really understanding. I learned a lot in this class. I'm really glad I took it. My semester would have been boring without it.

This course was genuinely interesting and easy to do well in if you do what the prof says. He is hilarious and entertaining, but also genuinely a good person who cares about your performance in the course. If you study what he tells you to, you will do well and the material isn't painful or difficult to learn! I would definitely recommend it!
best prof ever, genuinely a nice person and made difficult concepts easy to understand with the help of his everyday examples that relate closely to our generation.
A very nice prof. He's young and recently finished his schooling so he understands what it's like to be a student in this century.
Best prof ever! He is the first one I have ever met that cares so much about his students.
One of the best professors I have had at Queen's! He actually made a 3 hour lecture interesting!! He is so much fun and you learn so much! you will not regret taking his class.
It's a really good teacher. I love his class and the exam is not hard.
Prof Gauthier is really funny and relaxed in class, his lectures are interesting and is really approachable. The exams were pretty straightforward and were non cumulative.
best in class experience you will ever have.

He is a funny guy who manages to balence humour and care for your academic career. Honestly seems like one of the nicest people on campus. I would sign up with him if you want to have a really good time without needing to give much effort... Just take the class you fools.

You are awesome. More candy.

Il est un de mes professeurs préféré de mon parcours universitaire. Même si la matière du cours n'est pas la plus intéressante, il trouve un moyen de la rendre intéressante avec des effets sonores, des vidéos, etc. Il est drôle et souhaite vraiment que ses étudiants passe le cours. Les photos pour sa maman ou les vidéos de Rick Astley sont de mise!
Ce professeur a le don d'intégrer une touche d'humour à ses cours qui rend ses séances orignal, dynamique et intéressante.

"Yo! Ok.. Ça commence!" Le prof est très dynamique et toujours de bonne humeur. Il est très connaissant mais n'approfondira pas à moins d'une participation. 3 mi-sessions (quiz facile) et 1 dissert. finale 10p./40% sur le sujet de son choix. Il explique kindof mal mais compense dans sa correction si nécéssaire. À avoir 1 fois dans son bac.
Le cours le plus divertissant que j'ai suivi à l'université, le contenu du cours est ennuyant mais le prof le livre d'une manière exceptionnelle.

The course is boring, but the prof is great. He posts everything online and tells you the information you need to know for the tests. He is easily approachable, makes a lot of jokes, has a lot of energy, and is extremely nice. He gives 2 mini quizzes but the quizzes and tests are easy. I would take another class with him in a heart beat. He rocks.

By far the best prof I have ever had! He is absolutely hilarious! Every lecture is more entertaining than the last! This prof is so enthusiastic it's impossible not to be in a good mood when you get out of his class. He is very helpful and very organized and you know exactly what to expect on the exams.

Great Prof; always goes out of his way to try and make students laugh. Makes lectures fun and interesting with special effects and examples from popular media. Is literally there to make sure you succeed, and takes feedback seriously.  Posts his slides online, and has clear expectations about exams and mini-quizzes. 10/10 would recommend :)

He's a funny guy and is always making jokes in class and keeping things interesting, which can be difficult in a theory-based course. His accent is a bit hard to understand but it's nothing too severe. I find the class to be easy and classes are unnecessary to attend because he posts slides online and exams questions are taken straight from slides.

Prof Gauthier is very enthusiastic and will go out of his way to help you out. His teaching is interesting and engaging and his lectures are very funny. He makes sure you know what will be in the exam, so skipping class is definitely not recommended. He thankfully does not struggle with technology. Do recommend 10/10
